name: cleanbot-1
description: CleanBot is an innovative, low-cost AI-powered robot designed to autonomously detect, collect, and dispose of litter in various outdoor environments such as parks, beaches, and sidewalks. Equipped with a high-resolution camera and powered by the NVIDIA Jetson Nano, CleanBot processes real-time visual data to accurately identify trash items while intelligently avoiding obstacles, people, pets, and other non-target objects.
